  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Seven credibility factors are assessed; all achieved levels meet or exceed required levels under the accepted determination. Validation activities include bench-level flow loop experiments and particle image velocimetry comparisons against CFD-predicted velocity fields and hemolysis index values.",
