      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must have documented verification test suite and version-controlled source with traceable release notes.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used with full V&V test suite documentation and configuration management records satisfying MRL 5 SQA requirements."
    },
    {
