      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests on canonical benchmark cases must confirm expected spatial convergence rates.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to rotating-frame Navier-Stokes equations; second-order spatial convergence confirmed on three mesh refinement levels."
