      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions must be documented with traceability to calibrated instruments; deviations from COU conditions must be bounded.",
      "rationale": "Flow loop operated at 37 °C with bovine blood; inlet flow rate measured by calibrated Coriolis meter (±0.5%); rotational speed verified by optical tachometer. Conditions match COU operating envelope."
    },
