      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters must have documented sources and assigned nominal values with bounds.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity and density sourced from literature; hemolysis model constants from Giersiepen 1990. Uncertainty bounds on hemolysis constants not formally propagated — achieved level below required."
