      "acceptanceCriteria": "Number of experimental replicates must be sufficient to estimate measurement repeatability.",
      "rationale": "Five independent flow loop runs performed per operating point; coefficient of variation for NIH below 8% across all conditions confirming adequate sample size for repeatability estimation."
