      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameters applied in the simulation must match those measured during experiments within documented tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles derived from PIV measurements at pump inlet plane and applied as CFD boundary conditions; rotational speed matched to tachometer readings within 0.3%."
