    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Seven of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels; remaining six factors assessed at one gradation below required but within acceptable margin for the intended regulatory submission context. Validation results demonstrate hemolysis index predictions within 12% of bench measurements across all operating points. Panel accepts the simulation evidence as sufficient to support the hemolysis safety claim for the VAD COU.",
